{"tid":1211122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一隻狗放催淚彈可以擊退幾百人，但一隊遊擊小隊係遊客區可以浪費幾十警力","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T19:56:12.000Z","uid":17070,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9fa9b45834ff4f565dc1ff8c842aa2bbb1390d","tid":1211122,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本人極力支持警方，希望向警方提出線報</span></span><br />\n<br />\n岩岩係地鐵聽到人講呢番說話：<br />\n<br />\n「警力唔係無限，立法會多5個人作用係有，但如果呢5個人晏就係旺角/迪士尼呢d地方攪事就要浪費佢地幾十警力<br />\n立法會：1警with催淚彈 ko 300市民<br />\n遊客區：1游擊隊員 ko 10警<br />\n有事起上黎緊加可以即刻換一換個外表講普通話混入人混」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本人唔希望示威者轉移陣地，浪費香港警力<br />\n我愛祖國</span></span>"},{"pid":"72071ab11e23e9669367106835d0565300a391e5","tid":1211122,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f164c3f3dce1662fe5e7d676d38af31239be9dc","tid":1211122,"uid":191462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"一早都話要打遊擊"},{"pid":"a298d4610953e06376e31e017b1bc7591ab4c17f","tid":1211122,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f164c3f3dce1662fe5e7d676d38af31239be9dc","tid":1211122,"uid":191462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"一早都話要打遊擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"但唔係剩係金鐘中環一帶"},{"pid":"34053f0cf1a0815646d95573713fabc36a545f5a","tid":1211122,"uid":191462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a298d4610953e06376e31e017b1bc7591ab4c17f","tid":1211122,"uid":17070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f164c3f3dce1662fe5e7d676d38af31239be9dc","tid":1211122,"uid":191462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"一早都話要打遊擊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"但唔係剩係金鐘中環一帶"},"citedBy":0